<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Thanking" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Thanking,</orth> subst. gratitude: <cit><quote>the charge and t. shall be for me,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 3.5.101" default="NO" valid="yes">All's III, 5, 101</bibl></cit>. Plur. <emph>--s</emph> == thanks: <cit><quote>many and hearty --s to you both,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 5.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. V, 4</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>thank me no --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 3.5.153" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 5, 153</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>and graced the --s of a king,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 5.5.407" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 5, 407</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>